OL,3,C'Real concerns' about the workings of
OL,4,CJersey's construction industry
OL,6,FJersey's Competition Regulatory
OL,7,FAuthority (JCRA) says it has "real
OL,8,Fconcerns about how the construction
OL,9,Fsector operates" across the island.
OL,11,FScaffolding, aggregates and concrete,
OL,12,Fand residential construction will be
OL,13,Fclosely scrutinised going forward to
OL,14,Fensure price-fixing and anti-
OL,15,Fcompetitive practices are not taking
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,FIt comes as the economic regulator has
OL,19,Fconcluded their year-long
OL,20,Finvestigation into the industry.
