OL,3,C'Real concerns' about the workings of
OL,4,CJersey's construction industry
OL,6,FThe sector review was prompted by
OL,7,Fconcerns regarding the number of
OL,8,Fconstruction firms that have folded in
OL,9,Frecent years, despite the critical
OL,10,Frole the sector plays in the island's
OL,11,Feconomy.
OL,13,FStyle Group collapsed in August,
OL,14,Ffollowing the closure of Kalmac in
OL,15,FJuly 2024 and Camerons in 2023.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, several major construction
OL,18,Fprojects are underway, and other large-
OL,19,Fscale developments are forecast - such
OL,20,Fas the island's new acute hospital.
