OL,3,C'Real concerns' about the workings of
OL,4,CJersey's construction industry
OL,6,FThe JCRA's CEO, Tim Ringsdore, says
OL,7,Fthe research has given the regulator
OL,8,Freason to be very concerned about the
OL,9,Fworkings of construction firms, and he
OL,10,Fremains "committed to further
OL,11,Fsurveillance of the market".
OL,13,F"It isn't about pointing fingers", he
OL,14,Fadds. "It's about building a stronger,
OL,15,Ffairer sector."
