OL,3,C'Real concerns' about the workings of
OL,4,CJersey's construction industry
OL,6,FAlongside further investigation, the
OL,7,Fregulator will also start a programme
OL,8,Fof competition awareness sessions for
OL,9,Ftrade associations next year, and
OL,10,Fdevelop a set of guidelines that will
OL,11,Fallow businesses to collaborate safely.
OL,13,FMr Ringsdore adds that this
OL,14,Fcompetition is critical to the
OL,15,Fviability of the sector.
OL,17,F"Jersey needs a thriving construction
OL,18,Findustry to deliver homes,
OL,19,Finfrastructure, and jobs", he says.
